[style name="res://Dialogue/Styles/CozyPersonaVN.tres"]
[background arg="res://Art/Backgrounds/mayas_room.png" fade="0.7"]
The room is dimly lit. A desk lamp casts a warm glow over a cluttered study table.
Open textbooks. Printed reviewers. Half-finished thesis notes. Sticky notes cover the edges of Maya's laptop.
The wall calendar hangs nearby.
Almost every day has been crossed out.
The end of the term is only a few days away.
(Maya sits at her desk, staring blankly at her laptop.
The cursor blinks.
Waiting.
She doesn't type a single word.
She rubs her tired eyes.
Her phone lights up.
[signal arg="sfx:phone_notif"]
[signal arg="emotion_persist:nervous:2"]
A notification from the class group chat.
[signal arg="sfx:chat_flood"]
The class: MATE:"Guys, thesis progress update tomorrow."
Another message follows.
The class: MATE 2:"Pakisend na rin ng revisions before 10 PM."
Maya locks her phone without replying.
[signal arg="sfx:phone_lock"]
She leans back in her chair.
Letting out a long, exhausted sigh.
Hay...
She glances at the calendar.
Then at the mountain of schoolwork covering her desk.
Another sigh escapes.
Her eyes slowly drift toward the ceiling.
Silence.
She removes the chat notifications from her groupmates and pays her attention to videos she plays on an app.
The pinging continues...
Ping...
Ping...
Ping...
Annoyance is evident on her as her groupmates carry on talking.
She mutes the group chat itself and goes back.
[signal arg="sfx:chat_flood"]
[signal arg="emotion_persist:nervous:2"]
Goes back to scrolling to whatever she sees.
To calm the thoughts she holds inside.
The days continue to pass.
SCRATCH.
Another date is crossed out on Maya's calendar.
[background arg="res://Art/Backgrounds/classroom.png" fade="0.7"]
The professor lectures at the front of the room.
Most students type notes on their laptops.
Maya stares blankly at the presentation.
The lesson continues...
But her mind is somewhere else.
She remembers her first days of classes.
Asking what she wants to do in her life...
She knows deep down...
She shakes her head and listens to her prof.
She checks the time on her phone and sighs.
Still a long way to go.
[background arg="res://Art/Backgrounds/mayas_room.png" fade="0.7"]
Maya sits on her desk, on call with her thesis group.
Laptops are open.
Research papers are scattered across the table.
One of her groupmates checks their phone.
Another quietly packs up their laptop.
GROUPMATE 1Guys, may lakad kasi ako.
I'll finish my part mamaya na lang.
