Maya forces a small smile.
[signal arg="emotion_persist:sad:2"]
join Maya (neutral) left [animation="Instant In"]
Maya: Sige...
I'll handle it.
The groupmates leave.
The call ends.
Maya looks around her piled up table.
She slowly sighs.
Then begins working alone.
The clock reads 1:37 A. M.
Maya types continuously.
Her laptop displays the thesis document.
Several sections remain unfinished.
She decided to take a break and scroll a bit to ease her brain.
This makes her feel satisfied.
Until—
A notification appears.
THESIS GROUP CHAT
[signal arg="sfx:chat_flood"]
