"Reminder: Final draft due tomorrow."
update Maya (soft)
Maya immediately sighs.
The smile disappears.
She looks at the doodles and art hanging around her desk and walls.
Times were simpler back then, she misses it dearly.
She's deep in thought.
Why not give it a try again?
She opens her ipad and reveals the sketches she has made years back.
Her art account is still here, she can't believe it!
She goes back to the quiet hum of creating.
Her mind is at ease and she prefers it this way.
leave Maya [animation="Instant Out"]
[background arg="res://Art/Backgrounds/campus_hallway.png" fade="0.7"]
Maya walks alone.
Students excitedly discuss internships...
Graduation...
Future plans.
Their voices overlap as they pass by.
STUDENT 1Konti na lang, graduate na tayo.
STUDENT 2Sana makahanap agad ako ng trabaho.
Maya lowers her gaze.
