[background arg="res://Art/Backgrounds/mayas_room.png" fade="0.7"]
Maya sits at her desk.
A printed copy of her latest exam results.
She slowly picks up the paper.
Several grades are noticeably lower than before.
Maya quietly stares at them.
She grips the paper tighter.
Then folds it.
This course is taking a toll on her and she isn't sure this is what she wants...
She dismisses that thought.
She grabs the papers and starts hiding it beneath a pile of reviewers.
She knows she'll deal with that later.
She receives a text from her mother.
"Kain n, sabihan mu na rin tatay mu."
